Requirements:

* this source code
* node.js 0.2.6
* a modern browser, preferably Chrome
* add these lines to /etc/hosts
  127.0.0.1 example.com
  127.0.0.1 example.net


Let's get going:

* Fire up the server with 'node server.js'
  (for web sockets) also start the ws server with 'node ws_server.js'

* Navigate to http://example.com:4000


